  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "四",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_8631-8717",
          "range": "8631-8717",
          "rangeStart": 8631,
          "rangeEnd": 8717,
          "markText": "在现代历史中至少已经证明：任何政治斗争都是阶级斗争，而任何争取解放的阶级斗争，尽管它必然地具有政治的形式（因为任何阶级斗争都是政治斗争），归根到底都是围绕着经济解放进行的。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1769662747,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-01-29 12:59:07",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8631&rangeEnd=8717",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8631&rangeEnd=8717"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_11128-11202",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11128-11202",
      "markText": "头脑中发生这一思想过程的人们的物质生活条件，归根到底决定着这一思想过程的进行，这一事实，对这些人来说必然是没有意识到的，否则，全部意识形态就完结了。",
      "totalCount": 636,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11128&rangeEnd=11202",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11128&rangeEnd=11202"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_8538-8599",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8538-8599",
      "markText": "生产过剩和大众的贫困，两者互为因果，这就是大工业所陷入的荒谬的矛盾，这个矛盾必然地要求通过改变生产方式来使生产力摆脱桎梏。",
      "totalCount": 635,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8538&rangeEnd=8599",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8538&rangeEnd=8599"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_848-888",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "848-888",
      "markText": "鲍威尔只是在基督教起源史方面做了一些事情，虽然他在这里所做的也是一些重要的事情；",
      "totalCount": 625,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=848&rangeEnd=888",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=848&rangeEnd=888"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_2032-2072",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2032-2072",
      "markText": "它通过在《逻辑学》中详细探讨过并且完全包含在它自身中的一切预备阶段而向自身发展；",
      "totalCount": 573,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2032&rangeEnd=2072",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2032&rangeEnd=2072"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_2072-2141",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2072-2141",
      "markText": "然后它使自己“外化”，转化为自然界，它在自然界中并没有意识到它自己，而是采取自然必然性的形式，经过新的发展，最后在人身上重新达到自我意识；",
      "totalCount": 561,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2072&rangeEnd=2141",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2072&rangeEnd=2141"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_10189-10234",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10189-10234",
      "markText": "被压迫阶级反对统治阶级的斗争必然要变成政治的斗争，变成首先是反对这一阶级的政治统治的斗争；",
      "totalCount": 561,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10189&rangeEnd=10234",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10189&rangeEnd=10234"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_11031-11077",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11031-11077",
      "markText": "但是，任何意识形态一经产生，就同现有的观念材料相结合而发展起来，并对这些材料作进一步的加工；",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11031&rangeEnd=11077",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11031&rangeEnd=11077"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_6_2378-2413",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2378-2413",
      "markText": "对这些以及其他一切哲学上的怪论的最令人信服的驳斥是实践，即实验和工业。",
      "totalCount": 554,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2378&rangeEnd=2413",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2378&rangeEnd=2413"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_8_888-936",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "888-936",
      "markText": "施蒂纳甚至在巴枯宁把他同蒲鲁东混合起来并且把这个混合物命名为“无政府主义”以后，依然是一个宝贝；",
      "totalCount": 543,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=888&rangeEnd=936",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=888&rangeEnd=936"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_7_7475-7547",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7475-7547",
      "markText": "——真的，在费尔巴哈那里，爱随时随地都是一个创造奇迹的神，可以帮助他克服实际生活中的一切困难，——而且这是在一个分成利益直接对立的阶级的社会里。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300188773&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7475&rangeEnd=7547",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/244322f0813abb03dg0136bb?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7475&rangeEnd=7547"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300188773_6_1873-1982",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1873-1982",
      "markText": "例如在黑格尔那里，对这个问题的肯定回答是不言而喻的：我们在现实世界中所认识的，正是这个世界的思想内容，也就是那种使世界成为绝对观念的逐渐实现的东西，这个绝对观念是从来就存在的，是不依赖于世界并且先于世界而在某处存在的；",
      "totalCount": 464,
